values: Ok, i know its been like forever since i last posted anything but let me tell you, it wasn't because of laziness! I've just been busy being a gas station girl you know--well christina you wanted me to update so i'm updating! Do you see the power of you words!!!! Not much to say really---honestly, i'm a little dishearten at the moment. The world seems so out of balance and i just can't comprehend how anyone can justify the killings of nearly 400 people---its just tragic. Sorry didn't mean to get all  depressing on you its just my head is overflowing with alll these unfathomable questions.  well on a lighter note ---I maybe an Aunt, for the fourth time! -enjoy your Labor Day and may peace and tranquility find their way to your heart!
